CommunityType:c_5998.name: Schriber Ranch
CommunityType:c_5998.whatsNearbyDesc: Residents are just a short drive from great local amenities and attractions, including Camino Real Ranch event venue, Doc’s Drive-In Theater and more.
CommunityType:c_5998.overview: Schriber Ranch is a community of new single-family homes on half-acre homesites now selling in Mustang Ridge, TX. Situated a few miles south of downtown Austin off of SH-21 and SH-149, it offers a slower pace of life and expansive half-acre homesites soon to come. Amenities will include nearby trails and parks, while being in close distance to shopping and dining in San Marcos, Bastrop and Austin.
CommunityType:c_5998.shortIntroText: Schriber Ranch is the only community of new single-family homes on half-acre homesites in Mustang Ridge, TX, just 30 minutes from downtown Austin.
CommunityType:c_5998.amenityHeadlineText: See what life at Schriber Ranch has to offer
